{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dd439a7d8c","title":"四点指示（张春桥传达）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8eba251efd","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":17,"articleId":"dd439a7d8c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3be4d5766f","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题"},{"id":"714adabb18","name":"夺权和一月革命","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"24493ee3f0","type":"title","text":"四点指示（张春桥传达）","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd439a7d8c"},{"id":"c85150ecbb","type":"paragraph","text":"四点指示（张春桥传达）","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd439a7d8c"},{"id":"1367f4d054","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd439a7d8c"},{"id":"4183a67282","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.01.17  传达","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd439a7d8c"},{"id":"df2e5e6f6f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）今年搞文化大革命的指导思想是《红旗》和《人民日报》元旦社论，展开全面的阶级斗争。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd439a7d8c"},{"id":"f326e7acf3","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）要抓四个重点：北京、上海、天津、东北。责任是在造反派身上，要团结多数，造反派队伍要超过一倍以上。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd439a7d8c"},{"id":"48c8b68396","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）上海很有希望，许多学生、工人、机关干部起来了，这是当前文化大革命的形势。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd439a7d8c"},{"id":"7188c93205","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）红卫兵要向解放军学习，一定要朴素。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd439a7d8c"},{"id":"d2489e902e","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥还说：毛主席在元旦祝酒时说：“祝你们明年过社会主义关。”","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd439a7d8c"}],"page":{"id":"e0357dd7e9","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dd439a7d8c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}